claim.claim-text:
10. A medical or cosmetic therapeutic treatment according to claim 9, further comprising pretreatment steps of: 
administering an absorber; 
tuning said laser system to a specific absorption band of said absorber.

17. A medical or cosmetic therapeutic treatment in the thermal regime using a diode laser system comprising at least one laser diode emitter operating at a wavelength between 1000 nm and 1300 nm and emitting sufficient power to thermally destroy tumors and at least one means to optically transmit said emissions to a treatment site, comprising the steps of: 
administering an absorber; 
tuning said laser system to a specific absorption band of said absorber; 
selecting said treatment from a group consisting of coagulating, denaturing and shrinking tissue; and 
administering a radiation therapy treatment.

20. A medical or cosmetic therapeutic treatment in the thermal regime using a diode laser system comprising at least one laser diode emitter operating at a wavelength between 1000 nm and 1300 nm and emitting sufficient power to thermally destroy tumors and at least one means to optically transmit said emissions to a treatment site, comprising the steps of: 
administering an absorber; 
tuning said laser system to a specific absorption band of said absorber; 
selecting said treatment from a group consisting of coagulating, denaturing and shrinking tissue; and 
administering said treatment in combination with a radiation therapy treatment.
